  "prompt": "What's your favorite Friends episode? The one with the...?",
  "response": "Ah, it's so hard to choose just one \"Friends\" episode, but one that always stands out is **\"The One with the Embryos\" (Season 4, Episode 12)**! It's the one where Phoebe agrees to carry her brother\u2019s triplets, but the real highlight is the trivia game between the guys and the girls. The questions are hilarious, and Joey\u2019s \"Miss Chanandler Bong\" moment is iconic! Plus, Rachel and Monica lose their apartment to Chandler and Joey\u2014classic!\n\nHonorable mentions include **\"The One with the Prom Video\"** (Season 2, Episode 14) for that emotional Ross and Rachel moment, and **\"The One Where Everybody Finds Out\"** (Season 5, Episode 14) for the ultimate Chandler-Phoebe showdown (\"MY EYES! MY EYES!\").\n\nWhat about you? Got a favorite? \ud83d\ude0a",
